author: arkurth
msg: Added VMware.pm::find_datastore_files. It calls the OS module's find_files and prunes files under .snapshot directories. Changed calls in VMware.pm and vSphere_SDK.pm from find_files to find_datastore_files.
Updated vSphere_SDK.pm::get_registered_vms to detect "Unknown" VMs and not include them in the return array. This was causing many warning messages in vcld.log.
